<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">Voluntary idleness/laziness is not to be rewarded in any way. People do not have an inherent right to goods/services that they are not willing to work or pay for. Anything more than that is a blessing and a privilege.</p></body></html>